author: Hannah Bleau
title: Protesters Gather Outside of Kentucky Governor’s Coronavirus Briefing: ‘We Want to Work’
description: Protesters gathered outside of Kentucky Gov. Andy Beshear's (D) press briefing on Wednesday, shouting, "We want to work."
content:
Protesters gathered outside of Kentucky Gov. Andy Beshear’s (D) press briefing on Wednesday, shouting, “We want to work.”
